1.Dont use same variable names in query
      IN sims_login.PHP
      In select command - where password= '$password' is not working.
      Instead use where password='$pwd'.
      same  with userid.


2.Use and define $variables in same group ie inside same <?php ?>
  eg: <?php $classid=$_GET['class_id']; ?>
      <?php echo $classid; ?>

      the above code gives notice: undefined variable.
      Instead,
      <?php  $classid=$_GET['class_id']; 
             echo $classid;
      ?>
